head.title: Irish-Trad.net - Tablature
head.meta: Tablature for Irish Bouzouki/Mandolin/Octave Mandolin/Irish Tenor Banjo

familiarWithTab: For those more familiar with Tablature than standard music notation or ABC notation I have taken a number of tunes from TheSession.org and tabbed them out for both GDAE and GDAD.
clickingEachLink: Clicking on each link below will open the file in a .pdf format.
findTheseUseful: If you find these useful in anyway you should visit TheSession org and consider donating to the website. It has stood as a beacon for sharing and educating on musicians on traditional irish music for many years.
